sortMap() - Method in class hw7.bubbleSort
This method sorts the map using bubble sort The idea is to repeatedly swap adjacent keys if they are in the wrong order until the entire array is sorted.
sortMap() - Method in class hw7.insertionSort
This method sorts the map using insertion sort The idea is to iteratively insert each element into its correct position in the sorted part of the array.
sortMap() - Method in class hw7.mergeSort
This method sorts the map using merge sort The idea is to sort the keys of the map and then add the keys to the sorted map
sortMap() - Method in class hw7.quickSort
This method sorts the map using quicksort The idea is to select a pivot element and partition the array around the pivot so that all elements on the left are smaller and all elements on the right are larger.
sortMap() - Method in class hw7.selectionSort
This method sorts the map using selection sort The idea is to repeatedly find the minimum key in the unsorted portion and swap it with the first unsorted key.
